author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
In our most recent visit to Fonco Studios, Adam gets a tour of the prototyping shop, which is equipped with some of the latest full color resin printing machines. Fon Davis walks Adam through how they make use of full color prints to make miniatures for film and TV productions, and how their most advanced machine can even print full color dimensional textures on fabric!

Learn about Fonco Studio's projects and fabrication services at https://foncostudios.com/

Shot by Joey Fameli and edited by Norman Chan
Music by Jinglepunks
